rmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/9773/', '', 'Fluorouracil, Pemetrexed, Mercaptopurine, Cladribine, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Gemcitabine, Pralatrexate, Cytarabine, Decitabine, Azacitidine, Capecitabine', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Panitumumab, Obinutuzumab, Bevacizumab, Necitumumab, Dostarlimab, Ramucirumab, Atezolizumab, Amivantamab, More', 1767369485);
